data.description: Welcome Home to the Selle Valley! This captivating 10-acre property boasts a seasonal creek, mountain views, and outstanding features including a Farm House, Guest House, Wood Shop, Machine Shop, Two Garages, and a beautiful Classic Barn. The home is warm and inviting with a wood cook stove, upgraded gas range, 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, and an office. The oversized 2-car garage not only shelters vehicles but also houses the homes secondary power source (solar system controls and batteries). The 5400 sf barn is iconic and has hosted many weddings and other social functions. The machine shop and wood shop provide an additional 3200 square feet usable of space. Seize this one-of-a-kind opportunity and step into the dream lifestyle Selle Valley has to offer! *New mini-split for heating/air unit*
